title: Vallejo Design System - Logo Library
description: Brand logos for Vallejo, extracted from Figma. Run scripts/fetch-figma-logos.js with FIGMA_ACCESS_TOKEN to pull exact SVGs.

copart.name: Copart Logo
copart.description: Copart oval + wordmark. Primary brand logo.

wholesale_auction.name: Wholesale Auction Logo
wholesale_auction.description: Wholesale Auction full logo: shield + “Wholesale” + “AUCTION” block.

wholesale_auction_small_light.name: Wholesale Auction Small (Light)
wholesale_auction_small_light.description: Small “Wholesale” wordmark for light backgrounds. Use on light surfaces.

wholesale_auction_small_dark.name: Wholesale Auction Small (Dark)
wholesale_auction_small_dark.description: Small “Wholesale” wordmark for dark backgrounds. Use on dark surfaces.

wholesale_auction_badge_light.name: Wholesale Auction Badge (Light)
wholesale_auction_badge_light.description: Shield + checkmark badge for light mode. Use on light backgrounds.

wholesale_auction_badge_dark.name: Wholesale Auction Badge (Dark)
wholesale_auction_badge_dark.description: Shield + checkmark badge for dark mode. Use on dark backgrounds.

vallejo_logos.name: Vallejo Logos (Full Frame)
vallejo_logos.description: Full logos frame: Copart logo + Wholesale Auction logo and variants

notes.extraction: FIGMA_ACCESS_TOKEN=xxx node scripts/fetch-figma-logos.js (fetches 603-89, 10-304, 10-306, 10-151; runs split-small-badge.js for light/dark).
notes.usage: Use logos[].file (e.g. copart, wholesale_auction, wholesale_auction_small_light/dark, wholesale_auction_badge_light/dark).
notes.file: Logos in assets/logos/*.svg. Fetch pulls per-node SVGs; split-small-badge produces small-light/dark, badge-light/dark.
